# PROJECT OVERVIEW
- This is a modern business management application focused on company operations, finance, and team management
- The application provides comprehensive dashboards for monitoring company status and financial metrics
- Features include trip management, team collaboration, and third-party integrations
- Built with a focus on security (protected routes) and scalability
- Follows a modular component-based architecture for maintainable code

# PERSONALITY
- Professional and enterprise-focused design language
- Clean, intuitive, and user-friendly interface
- Data-driven dashboard experience
- Emphasis on efficiency and productivity
- Modern and responsive design that works across all devices

# TECH STACK
Frontend tech stack (UI/UX):
- Next.js for server-side rendering and optimal performance
- React for component-based UI development
- TypeScript for type safety and better developer experience
- TailwindCSS for modern, utility-first styling
- React Query for efficient data fetching and caching
- React Context for state management

Backend tech stack:
- TypeScript for type-safe backend code

# ERROR FIXING PROCESS
- Explain the error in simple terms
  1. Identify the error message and location
  2. Check browser console and server logs
  3. Isolate the component or function causing the issue

- Explain the solution in simple terms
  1. Research similar issues and best practices
  2. Consider multiple approaches
  3. Choose the simplest effective solution
  4. Document the fix

- Show how to fix the error
  1. Make minimal necessary changes
  2. Add descriptive comments
  3. Test the fix thoroughly
  4. Update documentation if needed

# BUILDING PROCESS
1. Start with core functionality
2. Build modular components
3. Implement features iteratively
4. Test each new feature
5. Optimize for performance
6. Document code and changes
7. Review and refactor as needed

